{"tid":305964,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"逼爆制服配透肉黑絲 陳庭欣扮港女空姐被鬧爆","createTime":"2017-07-02T07:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T06:19:12.000Z","uid":80183,"like":8,"dislike":187,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11d79a46f33fecf892df750e0b4e4bb934d11760","tid":305964,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"無綫劇集《迷》即將首播，宣傳片內出現上圍逼爆的陳庭欣（Toby）飾演港女空姐，除了造型吸引外，其「港女」演繹也成功成為網民熱話。<br />\n<br />\n 曾為2010年港姐冠軍的Toby，將於即將播映的無綫劇集《迷》中飾演港女空姐。宣傳片中，擁32.5C上圍的Toby穿上緊身空姐制服，並配上<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">透肉黑絲</span></span>，吸睛的造型成功吸引觀眾留意。其片中的「港女」演釋也引來網民討論，有網民指：「可能本性係咁，睇見都覺得乞人憎。」、「哈哈，做得幾好，可能因為做返自己。」「又JM tone又鍾意釣金龜，咪時下港女心態。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa621a192de3ce22823a42615d63efcc0e6dd573","tid":305964,"uid":108029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:01:14.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"86a588b67a558edaa42d453fc8e0b6034d35e41a","tid":305964,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"冇圖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d05b9a6c65046717c5c1cc5d0583c8b4719104e","tid":305964,"uid":80183,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖呢</blockquote><br />\n最憎伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b93c825d54aabcb74ee8b84915715bdef89052","tid":305964,"uid":43979,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>圖呢</blockquote><br />\n最憎伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAGGER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/de